  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a bard, you gain the following class features.</p>\n<h5>Hit Points</h5>\n<p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d8 per bard level</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 18 + your Constitution modifier</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d8 (or 5) + your Constitution modifier per bard level after 1st</p>\n<h5>Proficiencies</h5>\n<p><strong>Armor:</strong> Light armor</p>\n<p><strong>Weapons:</strong> Simple weapons, hand crossbows, longswords, rapiers, shortswords</p>\n<p><strong>Tools:</strong> All musical instruments</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Dexterity, Charisma</p>\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose any three</p>\n<h5>Equipment</h5>\n<p>You start one of the following equipment options, in addition to the equipment granted by your background:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A musical instrument, leather armor, a light crossbow with 20 bolts, two daggers, and a traveler's pack</li>\n<li>A musical instrument, two shortswords, a traveler's pack, and 5 gp</li>\n<li>100 gp worth of equipment and an equipment pack</li>\n</ul>",
